  <entry>
    <title>解决win10资源管理器(桌面任务栏)频繁假死</title>
    <url>/2022/05/06/20220506-0740/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><p><strong>最近装了ltsc2021,发现桌面和任务栏频繁假死，且无法呼出任务管理器，只得注销重新登陆，搜索了很久才在Microsoft社区找到了解决办法</strong></p>
<p>关于资源管理器假死的问题，建议您尝试以下方案：</p>
<p>1.打开任务管理器（或者点击CTRL+Shift+ESC）</p>
<p>2.点击“文件” - “运行新任务”</p>
<p>3.请确保勾选”使用管理员身份创建这个任务“</p>
<p>4.输入”Powershell” （忽略“”）</p>
<p>5.在Powershell中，输入以下两条命令并回车：</p>
<pre class=" language-powershell"><code class="language-powershell"><span class="token variable">$manifest</span> = <span class="token punctuation">(</span>Get<span class="token operator">-</span>AppxPackage Microsoft<span class="token punctuation">.</span>WindowsStore<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>InstallLocation <span class="token operator">+</span> <span class="token string">'\AppxManifest.xml'</span> <span class="token punctuation">;</span> Add<span class="token operator">-</span>AppxPackage <span class="token operator">-</span>DisableDevelopmentMode <span class="token operator">-</span>Register <span class="token variable">$manifest</span>
</code></pre>
<pre class=" language-powershell"><code class="language-powershell">Get<span class="token operator">-</span>AppXPackage <span class="token operator">-</span>AllUsers <span class="token punctuation">|</span><span class="token function">Where-Object</span> &amp;<span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">#123;$_.InstallLocation -like "*SystemApps*"&amp;#125;</span>
</code></pre>
<p>6.完成后关闭Powershell</p>
<p>7.重启您的计算机即可。</p>
<p>社区问题链接：<a href="https://answers.microsoft.com/zh-hans/windows/forum/all/win10%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%99%A8/41e4a6f7-7cd9-475e-8949-7ed50328949b?auth=1">传送门</a></p>
<p><img src="data:image/png;base64," data-original="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Alkaid114514/Pictures/main/imgs/202205060738695.png"></p>
]]></content>
      <tags>
        <tag>问题解决</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>解决禁用Microsoft商店自动更新后wsappx仍然运行的问题</title>
    <url>/2022/05/06/20220506-1741/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><p><em><strong>解决禁用Microsoft商店自动更新后wsappx仍然运行的问题</strong></em></p>
<p>解决方法：</p>
<p>在管理员PowerShell中输入命令卸载应M用商店</p>
<pre class=" language-powershell"><code class="language-powershell">Get<span class="token operator">-</span>AppxPackage <span class="token operator">*</span>WindowsStore<span class="token operator">*</span> <span class="token punctuation">|</span> Remove<span class="token operator">-</span>AppxPackage
</code></pre>
<p>再输入命令，重新安装商店</p>
<pre class=" language-powershell"><code class="language-powershell">get<span class="token operator">-</span>appxpackage <span class="token operator">*</span>store<span class="token operator">*</span> <span class="token punctuation">|</span> remove<span class="token operator">-</span>Appxpackage
</code></pre>
<p>再执行以下命令</p>
<pre class=" language-powershell"><code class="language-powershell">add<span class="token operator">-</span>appxpackage <span class="token operator">-</span>register <span class="token string">"C:\Program Files\WindowsApps\*Store*\AppxManifest.xml"</span> <span class="token operator">-</span>disabledevelopmentmode
</code></pre>
<p>之后打开商店再关闭自动更新即可</p>
<p>（此问题的原因似乎与系统更新有关）</p>
]]></content>
